<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/24597715">有哪些有趣又冷又恐怖的鬼故事？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2021181" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
