<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="573">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ifer-zhan" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ifer-zhan" class="zg-link" title="赵大飞">赵大飞</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$shen-shen-70-7" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/shen-shen-70-7" class="zg-link" title="甚甚">甚甚</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$hu-a-yue-42" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/hu-a-yue-42" class="zg-link" title="胡阿月">胡阿月</a></span>
